术讨论","title_alternative":"Life","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","stars":1033,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":557,"parent_node_name":""},"member":{"id":57901,"username":"ChefIsAwesome","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ChefIsAwesome","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/776c/7381/57901_mini.png?m=1445910196","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/776c/7381/57901_normal.png?m=1445910196","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/776c/7381/57901_large.png?m=1445910196","created":1394506521,"last_modified":1445910196},"last_reply_by":"cssk","last_touched":1674574550,"title":"老婆一年多没上班了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/910475","created":1674557695,"deleted":0,"content":"上一份工作干了三个月。上一份工作之前又是大半年不上班。连着几年都是这种上一阵子，歇半年一年的情况。她家里人不知道她上班是这个状态。\r\n\r\n我全职远程工作，家里饭是我烧，碗是随机我俩一人洗。洗衣服打扫卫生她也做，没那么勤快，总而言之是够不上家庭主妇的地步。\r\n\r\n年前我被老板优化了，本来不多的薪资砍了一半。\r\n\r\n现在我坐在老婆位于农村的家里受冻。有种要爆发的冲动。","content_rendered":"<p>上一份工作干了三个月。上一份工作之前又是大半年不上班。连着几年都是这种上一阵子，歇半年一年的情况。她家里人不知道她上班是这个状态。</p>\n<p>我全职远程工作，家里饭是我烧，碗是随机我俩一人洗。洗衣服打扫卫生她也做，没那么勤快，总而言之是够不上家庭主妇的地步。</p>\n<p>年前我被老板优化了，本来不多的薪资砍了一半。</p>\n<p>现在我坐在老婆位于农村的家里受冻。有种要爆发的冲动。</p>\n","last_modified":1674557695,"replies":30,"id":910475},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":21222,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2473,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":604427,"username":"Wannafl